#

Savory Pork Parmesan with Rich Tomato and Herb Meat Sauce

$18.5
720 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow CarbGluten-Free

Tags:

ItalianComfort FoodGourmet

Description

Succulent pork cutlets layered with melted cheese and a rich tomato-herb sauce, perfect for an indulgent meal.

Ingredients

  • Pork cutlets: 4 pieces
  • Parmesan cheese: 1 cup, grated
  • Mozzarella cheese: 1 cup, shredded
  • Olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Onion: 1 medium, diced
  • Tomato sauce: 2 cups
  • Crushed tomatoes: 1 cup
  • Fresh basil: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • Oregano: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Red pepper flakes: 1/2 teaspoon (optional)
